
Overview of verb mention

The verb mention has 3 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (62) mention, advert, bring up, cite, name, refer -- (make reference to; "His name was mentioned in connection with the invention")
2. (14) note, observe, mention, remark -- (make mention of; "She observed that his presentation took up too much time"; "They noted that it was a fine day to go sailing")
3. (6) mention, cite -- (commend; "he was cited for his outstanding achievements")
